{"tid":1694473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華記懺悔文","createTime":"2019-11-05T07:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T14:30:28.000Z","uid":197734,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e22d2a76a9747ade53c80ecce0b04ddd924a3506","tid":1694473,"uid":197734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"起初，<span style=\"color: gold;\">民眾爭取自由時，<br />\n我譴責了，因為上街示威是暴徒所為。</span><br />\n<br />\n當警察毒打民眾的時候，<br />\n我譴責了，因為警方武力是過分克制。<br />\n<br />\n當民眾舉辦喪禮的時候，<br />\n我譴責了，因為喪禮場合忌身穿黑衣。<br />\n<br />\n當DHL運送包裹的時候，<br />\n我譴責了，因為速遞公司竟運送黑金。<br />\n<br />\n最後當<span style=\"color: gold;\">政府來抓我時，<br />\n我譴責了，因我失去自由是奸人所害。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b87082eeea3b1e498c61e182c3b8aa87ffc1630","tid":1694473,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"參加罷工，但又驚冇左份工？<br />\n輪更制幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ZwcWhx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZwcWhx.jpg&h=f252a711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長期罷工效果<br />\n來同行，齊參與<br />\n返shift，射波<br />\n<br />\n邊日<span style=\"color: red;\">放假</span>/<span style=\"color: red;\">射波</span> 就好去遊客旺區振興經濟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊輪住嚟射波<br />\n入嚟集思廣益啦！<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE66GT2NXnPQ_tqDaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAE66GT2NXnPQ_tqDaA&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwIbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=c7a29321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE66GT2NXnPQ_tqDaA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MDhDR1TfFQfRVTi3299YuQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMDhDR1TfFQfRVTi3299YuQ&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwIbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=ef47b1c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla